<section class="container">

	<img class="img-fluid recipe-header-image" src="/images/{{recipe.recipeImage}}" alt="Card image cap">

	<h1>{{recipe.recipeTitle}}</h1>

	<p>Rub the steak all over with a good lug of olive oil and a good pinch of sea salt and black pepper. Add the steak to a hot
	pan, then cook for 6 minutes for medium-rare, or to your liking, turning every minute. For more flavour, try one or a combination
	of the following, and its ready to be eaten...</p>

	<h3>Instructions</h3>

	<div class="steps">
		{{{recipe.recipeProcedure}}}
	</div>

	<h3>Instructions</h3>

	<ol>
		{{#each recipe.Ingredients}}
			<li>{{quantity}} {{measurement}} {{name}}</li>
		{{/each}}
	</ol>
</section>